{"tid":1175315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：為無票港人打氣 德科隆市長 着佔中tee投票 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-05-28T12:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:58:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21b5f50233937ea07dd9d8fdc6c28104fedee457","tid":1175315,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190528/20689194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F20689194&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2N7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=1be429fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F20689194&h=211d8d1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190528/20689194</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：為無票港人打氣<br />\n德科隆市長 着佔中tee投票 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190528/large/28ls5p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190528%2Flarge%2F28ls5p01.jpg&h=198e7a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n着佔中tee去投票，Andreas Wolter不忘為港人送祝福。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n歐洲議會選舉啱啱喺星期日結束投票，投票率創咗20年新高。雖然呢件國際事件，好似同香港無關，但其中一位投票人，就將事件添上唔少香港色彩，皆因德國科隆市長Andreas Wolter當日着咗件寫有「和平佔中」字樣同標誌嘅tee為歐洲議會選舉投票，佢喺facebook留言，話藉此紀念所有其他地方無票可投嘅人，並將呢個問候送畀喺中國同香港嘅朋友，認真有心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190528/large/28ls5p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190528%2Flarge%2F28ls5p02.jpg&h=97017dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱牧當年領獎時舉黃傘，Andreas Wolter（右）在場見證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190528/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190528%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=58cea581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n朱牧16年所贈<br />\n<br />\n到底佢呢件佔中tee，喺邊度得嚟？查實係同佔中案被告之一、獲判緩刑嘅朱耀明有關。仲記唔記得朱牧喺2016年獲德國福音基督教會科隆市基督教教區頒授Pfarrer-Georg-Fritze紀念獎呢？當時朱牧就送咗呢件tee畀市長做紀念品，朱牧都話估唔到，對方會喺歐洲議會投票時着呢件tee，覺得意義好大，而當年朱牧攞獎時即席舉黃傘，Andreas Wolter都喺現場見證。<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：走光黑點 戲曲中心西九站上榜 (李八方)"},{"pid":"94d75bbb9782721d1c8acbd7e56f4cf179b7d8b1","tid":1175315,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:58:04.000Z","msg":"好想做德國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}